column7: ["I am disappointed because the screen has a few deep scratches, with that being said with a screen protector on it they're pretty much unnoticeable. The battery was completely drained so I had to wait about an hour and a half to set it up. Item description said no blemishes. Other than that I am pleased with the phone. It arrived in a timely manner.", 'I was happy when I checked the phone and it was legit. I have been ripped off twice and I am happy you were not the third. Thank you for the phone it came in 1 piece, I wish it had a charger but I had a spare. Looks and works brand new.', 'The phone looks like brand new without any scratch despite is open box item. It equally arrived on time. I have not using the phone due to my inability to transfer all my information from the faulty phone to this phone. I hope by weekend will be able to put the phone into use. I will reach out once I start using the phone but all the same the phone look excellent from the appearance.', 'Good phone, as described, works very well, battery is in good shape. Happy.', "This phone is great!the size of the phone is perfect. For a new model phone, the price can't be beat. It works perfectly on AT&T. It didn't come with any accessories or an original box but that's OK. There was very minor cosmetic blemishes along one side but nothing to complain about. Everything I've tried to use works and it has updated to OS 14. So overall, very pleased! 5 stars.", 'Great product. works perfectly. Looks brand new. Will buy from again.', "This is a gift so the phone won't be setup and checked out with an account for a couple weeks but, so all is as advertised. Arrived on time, the exterior is in Mint condition and the battery charged to 100% with no issue. Will update on phone performance after the account setup.", "The phone is in relatively good shape. An inch long scratch in glass prevents me from describing it's condition as excellent.", "Phone arrived just in time, no scratches on the phone, it's good enough for basic task, the screen it's good for movies, and battery life manages to be efficient during the day. Would recommend if you want a phone for your every day life.", "The phone was great it just didn't bring power cord nice phone nice size", 'Nice Cell Phone Works Perfect ! Shipping took a long time, No fault of Fone Logics as I was a big storm in Houston Texas.', 'Great product arrived on time and looks brand new.', 'The screen had minor scoffs but not visible once a screen protector is applied.', 'The phone is Perfect. HOWEVER, of no fault to FoneLogics the shipping was seriously elongated as a result flooding and weather condiitons across the country. 2.5 weeks from initial order and receipt. Hmm', 'Phone was in perfect condition. Everything works. Fast shipping.', 'Happy with product, shipping took alot longer than expected, but was not the sellers fault, received product in excellent condition.', "Great price, Super speedy shipping. This is just the phone. There is nothing else that comes with it. No charge adapter, no users manual, nothing. Just the phone. But that's all I needed.", "Phone wasn't quite as described. I suspect these are refurbished and not open box. See photos of the wear to the phone. That said, it shipped quick and was a reasonable price for a used phone.", 'Phone works great. Delivered in great condition. If I had one complaint no box, charger kinda of a bummer.', 'Great product and fantastic shipping along with price. Seller is a pleasant business to do a purchase with and stands 100% behind their products.', 'Great phone great condition and very fast shipping seller also will help resolve any issues if any', 'The phone was as described and a huge upgrade from where I was with an A12. I did have to contact the seller and they were prompt and helpful with responses. The phone arrived late, but not because of the seller. It was shipped quickly, but USPS dropped the ball. I would purchase from this seller again.', 'Everything came perfectly as stated. I was worried about this being a hokey scam but everything came back perfect, using the phone to type this out and have not had a problem with it at all. 10/10 would recommend!', 'I received the product, from first assessment, it went well. Good product', 'Thanks! Fits great on my phone.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '']

column7: ["The phone just looks perfect. It's the aesthetic beautiful phone as promised. It used my sim card, mobile net and wifi perfectly. The pictures it takes are great quality, the touchpad feels incredible! However I had a huge problem. It was constantly freezing and the battery didn't want to charge. I'm sad having to send it back, since this is my dream phone. But the seller was incredibly nice and polite, paid me back everything, paid for the return post fees as well. I recommend this seller!", 'Phone is in very good condition Fast shipping Good communication with dealer For this price it doesn’t make sense to buy a new phone In Poland it does work without any issues Phone is very good Japanese quality You can’t make anything wrong with buying this device I love it It’s stylish Satisfying to use Probably does have a better antenna than my iPhone Metal abs plastic and glass combined', "amazing condition! it doesn't even look used not a single scratch or imperfection! unfortunate that it doesn't seem to be compatible with any U.S carriers but i love it regardless. it took about 3 weeks to be delivered but it was worth the wait, seller is very responsive, would definitely buy from here again :)", "got here SUPER fast! Item was pretty much exactly how it was described. I will note, *this does not work on north American carriers*, but I knew this getting into it! The battery life is short but that's to be expected, since its not really a phone youre gonna have screen-on all day. No complaints, got exactly what I ordered. if I TRIED to complain, it could have been nice to have had software updates done (since this requires a USIM), but thats a nitpick. Would buy from this seller again!!", 'Order arrived earlier than expected and it was in great condition! Phone works perfectly! It has some very minor scratching, something expected with a used product, but nothing too visible. Overall, excellent seller and product!', "Arrived way earlier than expected which was a nice surprise. The packaging made me nervous at first because the phone was only wrapped in one thin layer of bubble wrap and then put inside an envelope - but when I opened it, the flip phone was working just fine! Some scratches, a few chipped corners, and dirt but I expected it anyway as a long-time tech thrifter (just clean it with alcohol and you'll be fine). Happy with my purchase, thank you.", "The device looks new. little scratch but its manageable. although the phone flip is damage it was hard to close i just put rubber to keep them close 🥲. but no expectations its a 2nd hand phone so i think it was ok for my first flip phone. The seller is hard to chat its like im talking to myself he/she just reply once and didn't reply to my inquiry. Anyway thats all. 🥲. Thanks for the phone...🥲❤️🥲❤️🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲📱📱📱❤️❤️❤️🙏🏻🧿💭🥤✔️🌸🎉🎈🫠🫠🫠🫠🫠🫠", 'The seller was extremely friendly and responded quickly to all my inquiries. The phone works perfectly in Sweden with a Comviq SIM. If the phone asks for a PIN, the seller is very quick to assist. column7: ["Recently purchased a brand new Samsung Galaxy S21 Ultra from your platform and am extremely impressed with the device. The phone's performance, camera quality, and overall design are top-notch. The shipping was fast and the packaging was secure, ensuring the device arrived in perfect condition. I appreciate the smooth transaction and would definitely recommend your platform to others. Thank you for providing such a great product and service.", 'I ordered a brand new Samsung Galaxy S21 Ultra 5G 998U phone from Diamond Wireless Deals. Even though it cost $4 more than from other sellers it was totally worth it because they offered and provided a much more speedy delivery compared to sellers in the USA and especially sellers in China. The phone is exactly what I ordered and works great!', 'Quick shipping. Product was new in box, but the box was not shrink-wrapped(so it was an open(ed) box). Very happy with the seller’s quick shipping and with what I received. This phone purchase was my attempt to get the “newest” Galaxy phone that allows an SD card. The received Galaxy S21 Ultra 5G does not allow an SD card, but I will keep it anyway.', "The phone was new, but not unlocked. It shows up as a verizon phone. My carrier (tello) is working fine so I do not have a problem. I am also curious as to why a 'new' samsung phone has no warranty.", 'I just received my phone, I’m not satisfied because the phone doesn’t match up with the description. It’s not New phone as described, it has scratches and package not sealed. No adapter is included only charger.', 'So far I love the phone. It was, however, advertised wIth an S pen and there is S pen settings. Where is the S pen?', 'Item new in box. Perfect condition. Works great. Service works with the phone. Easy and smooth transaction. Thanks much! A++', 'Workes great and perfect condition and fast shipping,', 'Decent phone, just a little big to fit in pocket.', 'Great phone! Luv the crisp image display. Box was open however the phone is pristine. Very fast shipping. Phone in hand within 3days after paying . 👍', 'Good phone, received quickly. Did have yo flash the firmware so it would update. Works fine now.', 'Its a very fast unit. Not a scratch on it. Nice.', 'Perfect condition. Works as indicated.', '⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ Perfect EBay experience! Despite an initial mix-up, this seller’s communication and prompt rectification ensured that we received the exact item we had hoped for; a BRAND NEW, sealed Samsung S21 Ultra, unlocked, with 512GB of storage. Highly recommend this seller and wouldn’t hesitate to shop with them again. Thank you!', "This phone came in an opened box and the screen and camera didn't work properly from the start. They claim its a new phone but it operated just like a refurbished. Only had it a few days and the back and screen cracked in my pocket even though it was in a case. They refused to give me a replacement saying it was somehow my fault. Horrible product. Horrible customer satisfaction.", 'This was returned due to its not unlocked. But overall the product is good.', 'The phone works great but I had to flash the OS because it would not download updates no matter what I tried.', 'Beautiful brand new phone! I love it. The color is way more gorgeous than I expected and I am delighted 😊. Ty! Great seller! Fast shipping.! Highly recommend 👌.', 'New as advertised. Charged it up and ready to go. Quick delivery.', 'Very nice phone just like the description. Without any blemishes, but missing charger.', 'SATISFECHO,, LO RECIBÍ,, TAL,, Y; CÓMO LO PEDÍ,,, MUCHÍSIMAS GRACIAS; (DIAMOND WIRELESS DEALS),, ES MUY BONITO DISEÑO,, ES UN ESPECTACULAR TELÉFONO CELULAR 📲,,, LO ÚNICO QUE NO LE ENCONTRÉ FUE EL CABEZAL PARA CARGARLO,, SÓLO SALIÓ EL CABLE NADA MÁS…..', 'Beautiful phone, zero issues after 5 days use. Everything from old phone copied over in less than 10 minutes after switching out the sim card. Would recommend and buy from this user in the future.', 'phone worked great, but had issues with GPS so I had to return it. :( seller:10/10, the item was new and arrived quickly', 'The phone is not new as the seller claims. I will definitely use them again for my next upgrade.', 'Parece que el celular salió defectuoso de pronto la pantalla dejó de funcionar lo positivo es que tube un rembolso completo y el embio de regreso gratis', "Phone appears new as described. As an upgrade from my note 9, I'm enjoying the added features without learning a whole new phone. I've noticed a couple little glitches though. One being that sometimes the screen goes dim and to get it back normal, I have to close it down and reopen the screen. So far it's a good purchase.", 'Phone arrived in excellent condition. Thanks so much for putting it up for sale. My son was looking for this for a long time so I could update my old Samsung Galaxy and was pleasantly surprised to find this at such a good price.', "I'll admit I was a bit skeptical about it being a new Note 20. It came in all original packing, had the stylus, new factory charger, & had the factory protective screen covering. I had a Note 20 prior that got damaged. Everything transfered & life is good again.", 'A++ Seller. Phones came fast, took awhile for us to get activated. The phones are brand new, and a very good price. Working great.', "It was not New phone, and it was not sealed. I think the screen has been changed too. I don't recommend.", 'I ordered item on 2/8 and received it on 2/10. Phone is in excellent condition and works just fine. Five stars!', 'Super fast shipping.....phone was brand new and works great', 'I been using this cell phone for over a week and it works great. I am very happy with my purchase. The price is right. I highly recommend.', 'Galaxy note 20 5g came brand new with charger and cable, headphones. Battery hold charges like a brand new phone. A+++ will buy again soon.', 'was a bit worried at first but excellent buy thank you i was a bit skeptical about the box but it all is great brand new as advertised thanks again', "Not new, clearly a refurb. There is visible debris inside the camera lens. Aftermarket stylus. Serial lookup shows it was bronze, now it's green. Although not carrier locked, it's not factory unlocked, it's verizon firmware. I haven't disassembled it yet, but judging by the side by side with my oem Note 20, it's an aftermarket display.", 'Great product and business phone is exceptional and works perfectly fast delivery too very happy', "Ordered on Saturday and received it on Wednesday. Received the phone exactly as described. New mint condition in the box with all of the accesories. Was able to swap out the Missus' SIM card and had it all set up, full-charged, and making calls/texts in under 30 minutes.", 'Nice phone. As described. Works great.', "Despite its appearance as a brand-new item, closer inspection reveals otherwise. Discrepancies include a mismatched serial number on the box, misalignment on the internal camera ring, and the brushed aluminum sides appearing to be replaced with OEM parts. I suspect that if I were to open it up, I might find a third-party battery. While it offers great value, I don't believe it is truly 100% brand new.", "I am giving 4 stars instead of 5 because this was sold to me as new phone but I don't think it was new. If it had been described as almost new, I would not have bought it. There was no film covering the front of the phone and the accessories were loose in the box. Maybe the battery is bad because I have to charge it to 100% twice a day. It doesn't hold a charge 24 hours.", 'Perfect. Love the size, quality and color. Fast shipping.', 'Phone arrived before promised, in excellent condition, and works better than expected.', 'seems to work good,would by again,good seller.', 'Good Product, Excellent Price and Fast Shipping A++', "Wonderful eBuying experience. Great item that was exactly as described. Packaged well with f-a-s-t shipping. Doesn't get any better than that.
